latestIgtvVideos.title: WittyVows X SimranTakkar DIY Wedding Makeup Tutorial 💗✨ Glam Eyes
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We partnered with Ace Bridal Makeup Artist Simran Takker to help bring you an easy wedding look that you can do on your own for your wedding! In the immediate future, weddings will be intimate, Simran’s forecast is for brides to wear elaborate outfits and jewellery but how subtle on their makeup. She’s sharing one neutral and easy look that brides can DIY for the wedding it pre wedding functions incase they don’t get a professional mua. ✨✨✨✨✨
What you need : 
highlighter (mac nylon) 
Peach eyeshadow in two shades 
Brown eyeshadow 
Pencil liner
A set of medium lashes and glue 
Nude eye pencil 
Pigmented grey shadow 
Glitter

latestIgtvVideos.title: Most romantic surprise proposal at cafe tesu for a 1 year anniversary
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This is what boyfriend dreams are made of. Aarushi’s boyfriend not only proposed to his girlfriend in the cutest way, he also recreated the same proposal a year later for their anniversary! “Inspite of being in the same college we never spoke to each other, just the casual hi’s and hello’s sometimes! I came out of a bad relationship and he decided to text me on instagram and we started talking over guitars and music, me being fond of it and he being a guitarist! We started talking a lot but only over the texts! For 2 months straight, we were talking on whatsapp and since vacations were going on, we didn’t get the chance to meet! Gradually we started talking over calls! There wasn’t a single day where we didn’t talk! He used to sing songs over the phone, lullabies not only at night but even whenever i used to take my naps in the day! I don’t know when did i start falling for him! 
College reopened, we decided to meet for the 1st time on the 6th of September, and yes thats the day of the proposal! The first day we met, he asked me out! Gutsy no? This is a video of September 2018, where he recreated what he did in 2017 to celebrate the completion of 1 year!”
